issue.title: Can support putting image on the right?
issue.body:

There are some scenarios where you need to put the icon on the right.

**For example**
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/23382969/53708794-0739d280-3e70-11e9-95b2-e433e3bd74c8.png)

comment.body:
Hey @CaliCastle thanks for your awesome repo.
I would like to put the icons on the right, I searched and I didn't find a way to do it, is that possible?
